Halucigen pulled a quick maneuver pulling up then flipping around
above the beast as he snapped."ahh" he squealed.
He transformed into a small disabled scorpion missing two of his legs
landing on the back of Prowl. He whipped his stinger forward shooting
an acid to burn a small hole through the armour of Prowl.
"if i can stay on long enough to get a virus bot into him i could slow
him down...i hope...."
